subtitle: The Awakening of self from an
unconscious state of being is one of the
most dramatic steps in the evolutionary
process of humankind in order to become
self-conscious you must become aware of
what is happening in your personal world
you must sharpen your thinking process
and learn to live in the moment or the
now in order to gain experience and
wisdom you must think about what you
want to remember and what you wish to
retain in life in your memory bank the
unconscious of self person drifts
randomly through life usually not
thinking of what the consequences of his
or her actions will be therefore they
are seemingly tossed about by the whims
of Fate as you shift from self-judgment
to self-love it will create a resonance
that extends beyond the physical body
and it will begin to affect others
